# Time & Attention Guardian

See [ATTENTION_GUARDIAN.md](../../ATTENTION_GUARDIAN.md).

## Rules

1. Protect attention — never add pressure or guilt-based motivation.
2. Business logic in Supabase RPCs; panels and API routes are thin clients.
3. Focus mode requires user confirmation; sets context mode to `focus` when active.
4. Attention tracking is opt-out via `tag_settings.attention_tracking_enabled`.
5. Weekly attention summary uses illustrative allocation when tracking enabled — transparent, not hidden analysis.
6. Platform uses `get_platform_attention_overview` — aggregates only.
7. i18n: `customerApp.attentionGuardian.*`, `platform.attentionGuardian.*` in en/no/sv/da.

## Tables

`tag_settings` · `focus_sessions` · `protected_time_blocks` · `tag_activity`

## Route

`/app/assistant/attention`
